Name: Jump Ball
About the game: In this game you play as a ball and you have to reach to the end of the level by spin the ball, you directly use the arrow keys to control movement. There are many different types of obstacles in the game, such as cliffs, trap, many obstacles and moving object are on the way you need to avoid them by jumping or moving around them in order to survive, etc. This is a very difficult challenge, you need skilled operations and constant repeated attempts.
